AbandonedShip_Corridors_1F_Text_CharliePostBattle:
	.string "It's not easy throwing Pok√© Balls\n"
	.string "while hanging on to an inner tube!$"

AbandonedShip_Corridors_1F_Text_IsntItFunHere:
